{"word":"καθήκω","slug":"καθήκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαϑήϰω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἥκω\">ἥκω</a></el>; ‘come down to, come to’] <b>be proper/fitting,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ impf.\">impf.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pres.\">pres.</a> sense: <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐ\">οὐ</a> ϰαϑῆϰεν αὐτὸν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ζῆν\">ζῆν</a></el> it’s not fitting for him to go on living <b><a href='B:510 22:22'>Ac 22:22</a>;</b> <el>ποιεῖν τὰ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μὴ\">μὴ</a> ϰαϑήϰοντα</el> do what is improper <b><a href='B:520 1:28'>Ro 1:28</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καθηγητής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κάθημαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}